took a cruise. He told me he had met you, and

20:09.494 --> 20:27.100
he had intimated with sometimes in the 30s, and 
then when I was listening to the tape, I couldn't

20:09.494 --> 20:27.100
figure out when it was because I couldn't put you 
two together anyplace, you see, because you just

20:09.494 --> 20:27.100
say your assignments, woods, holes. and, you 
know, and the University of Washington. So I never

20:30.299 --> 20:35.486
really got you somehow in the, when I was looking 
you up, I never really somehow got you into the

20:30.299 --> 20:35.486
Navy. You know, it didn't make any sense to me. I was 
actually in the Coast Guard. Called me in the Coast

20:40.093 --> 20:40.894
Guard. Yeah, but I worked with the Navy. And I was in 
a very unique and satisfying position. And so I

