23:04.610 --> 23:10.455
people, early people. Norris Raikstra would come 
down on weekends. Big load. He was pretty well

23:16.301 --> 23:22.127
entranced at Harvard by that time, and hardly 
ever. ever got down, but we did. Mary Sears was

23:25.192 --> 23:39.488
there,

