23:47.257 --> 23:51.422
was, I don't know whether it was I just can't place 
it in 1933 or 1934

23:51.723 --> 24:11.665
that he was up in Alaska and had met him then.

24:14.428 --> 24:18.473
And Dick Fleming, I met I don't know what he calls it 
or not, when he was up here with Moberg, I think, one

24:20.039 --> 24:37.189
time when we had a either Pacific Science 
Convention here in Seattle or something like

24:20.039 --> 24:37.189
that. And Tommy Thompson, you see, worked with the 
people at Scripps. He worked with McKeown. in

24:44.204 --> 24:58.379
1929, in the Gulf of Alaska, on the currents, and 
Van Cleve was one of our, that was out on the cruise

24:44.204 --> 24:58.379
there. So it was this time, about that time that I 
met him.

