take the shortcut, time a little bit through the 
Gulf of St. Lawrence, through the Strait of Belle

30:11.731 --> 30:21.853
Isle, and his ship was lost with all hands from 
icing conditions in the Gulf of St. Lawrence. That

30:22.054 --> 30:26.183
was Lafarge, Mrs. Island's brother. So that was a 
blow to me and to Columbus, I know.

